202, "postdatetimestamp": 1768401645}, {"pid": 854610470, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 68, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-14 22:42", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "在目前4000以上的市场，说实话我也是小心翼翼，我只能靠纪律约束自己，因为我知道，最大的亏损来自于盲目自大的操作，4000以上的行情没多少人做过的，何况是和以前完全不一样的市场，都要摸索", "lou": 82, "content_length": 178, "from_client": "8 Android", "postdatetimestamp": 1768401761}, {"pid": 854611400, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 70, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-14 22:52", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854610876,45974302,184]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66989363]鱼饵啊啊[/uid] (2026-01-14 22:47):[/b]<br/><br/>感谢狼大提醒， 量能这么大，会不会gjd也是在找感觉。[/quote]<br/><br/>大家都是第一次 这波国家队和以前不一样我说过很多次了<br/>今天在纯技术卖点配合盘中消息，尾盘还用红利压盘，再结合前天的监管加大，这些操作表明他们在一步步的使用工具和手段小心的维护市场，不然以前的一刀切又不是没见过<br/>所以我觉得我们大家也要配合，一起营造十年长牛不好么，谁还想过回以前一天5000E成交半死不活的市场？你愿意么", "lou": 83, "content_length": 312, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 854610876, "postdatetimestamp": 1768402355}, {"pid": 854612434, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 44, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-14 23:03", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854611975,45974302,185]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=1353185]等爬墙的红杏[/uid] (2026-01-14 22:58):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，为什么放出来后开新帖你这么活跃。以前可是好几天不发言是常态。这个点儿还看你这么频繁发言，好不习惯[/quote]<br/><br/>还好吧，主要是今天这种走势我也没见过，需要仔细复盘每一个细节，看看大家都没有别的见解和消息是我没有注意的 你们聊你们的<br/><br/>还有美股现在也映射我们的开盘的 毕竟4WE成交的市场谁敢忽视", "lou": 84, "content_length": 176, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 854611975, "postdatetimestamp": 1768403036}, {"pid": 854613045, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 38, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-14 23:11", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854612842,45974302,185]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=61395264]村上吹树[/uid] (2026-01-14 23:08):[/b]<br/><br/>我就是这种没看懂，为什么要压这些白马权重股？why？因为只有这些有筹码？那资金肯定也不去这些板块了。那资金明天会去哪里呢？继续挑战还是泥沙俱下？继续挑战的话，我直接全面砍掉三分之二仓。泥沙俱下我倒不怕。最后的结果就是希望资金能来低位轮动或者向业绩这块走，不然大盘短期就A下去了。[/quote]<br/><br/>因为不能压券商 这是进攻确认风向标，如果压了券商就不是降温了，是招呼大家结束了，毕竟今天出来的政策已经利空券商了，所以只能压红利，国家队有筹码的方向不多", "lou": 85, "content_length": 155, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 854612842, "postdatetimestamp": 1768403469}, {"pid": 854616156, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 22, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-14 23:46", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854615695,45974302,187]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67046194]1nvix[/uid] (2026-01-14 23:40):[/b]<br/><br/>但是券商ETF今天午盘开盘直接开砸喔，搞不懂[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>。。。这个消息第一利空就是券商", "lou": 86, "content_length": 35, "reply_to": 854615695, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768405588}, {"pid": 854643772, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 48, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-15 09:55", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "缩量才能止跌 是好事。", "lou": 87, "content_length": 20, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768442124}, {"pid": 854644954, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 84, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-15 10:03", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854644484,45974302,197]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38754660]消费机的逆袭[/uid] (2026-01-15 09:59):[/b]<br/><br/>狼哥真牛，希望每天能指点一个板块。[/quote]<br/>。。。。。。。。。。你们是不是要求过高了？匹配不上自己的用处啊。。。", "lou": 88, "content_length": 73, "reply_to": 854644484, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768442587}, {"pid": 854645670, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 87, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-15 10:07", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854645249,45974302,198]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67046194]1nvix[/uid] (2026-01-15 10:05):[/b]<br/><br/>想问问狼大，图哥真的不回来了嘛[s:ac:哭][/quote]<br/>你管他做什么  逻辑没变  你指望他和你们说点位么？他敢说 你们也敢信?", "lou": 89, "content_length": 66, "reply_to": 854645249, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768442858}, {"pid": 854647110, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 34, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-15 10:16", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "对了  贵金属板块可以重新观察，不是说要买<br/>但是贵金属板块今天走了补涨+避险  居然回到逻辑内了，不知道是不是里面资金都清楚应该什么时候做什么了。", "lou": 90, "content_length": 135, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768443398}, {"pid": 854648571, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 9, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-15 10:26", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854647641,45974302,201]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=62771233]极地丶之光[/uid] (2026-01-15 10:20):[/b]<br/><br/>话说狼大对于今年铜涨价的事情怎么看？个股一直在天上都下不来[/quote]<br/>我做的是期货  期货没完 股票我没做 观察而已 江铜质量很高", "lou": 91, "content_length": 55, "reply_to": 854647641, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768443982}, {"pid": 854648939, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 20, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-15 10:28", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854648022,45974302,201]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=9032340]letuswowing[/uid] (2026-01-15 10:22):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大 液冷为什么今天动了<br/>硬的大哥们都在水下呢[/quote]<br/>液冷的基本逻辑我没说过吗<br/>我AI硬的底仓目前是锁仓的 不打算加 也不会动", "lou": 92, "content_length": 69, "reply_to": 854648022, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768444114}, {"pid": 854649711, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 22, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-15 10:33", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854649375,45974302,202]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=61422464]kaiserDu[/uid] (2026-01-15 10:31):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，4096感觉会破~[/quote]<br/>有什么所谓 你知道这几天抢开融资的 等着4079-4090进场的有多少么。回归业绩就行了", "lou": 93, "content_length": 80, "reply_to": 854649375, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768444398}, {"pid": 854650191, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 52, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-15 10:36", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "对了 你们有固态的 电池是一个轮动行情 是我在这波调整里面避险的一个方向，我后面还是会回归主线趋势的，不过这几天还是能玩玩", "lou": 94, "content_length": 116, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768444575}, {"pid": 854651536, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 23, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-15 10:44", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854651431,45974302,204]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=9032340]letuswowing[/uid] (2026-01-15 10:44):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大 机器人打算几月份在做<br/>做完半导体之后么？<br/>感觉机器人调整的差不多了[/quote]<br/>我没有这个感觉", "lou": 95, "content_length": 19, "reply_to": 854651431, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768445080}, {"pid": 854652461, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 29, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-15 10:50", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854651966,45974302,204]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=6313142]暮残[/uid] (2026-01-15 10:47):[/b]<br/><br/>跟隔壁黄金楼的思路<br/>去年下半年开始，铜的逻辑我觉得是非常硬的<br/>美元跌传导到黄金涨 到大宗重新定价，中国缺铜/美国缺铜，铜扩产周期长<br/>黄金保守看到5000，那铜的逻辑我觉得甚至比铁盒都硬<br/>从长持角度看，每次回调都是上车的机会<br/>以上发言是我32卖飞紫金后痛定思痛的结论[/quote]<br/>做期货才有意义 我黄金多单和铜多单都长持 银确实不敢做了<br/>逻辑没有变化 大放水时代 <br/>股票也就是今天他们重回逻辑我才关注，不然根本不好做 天天跳空高开下砸你愿意？", "lou": 96, "content_length": 153, "reply_to": 854651966, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768445415}, {"pid": 854654038, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 43, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-15 11:00", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854653118,45974302,205]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=61653072]学装机吧[/uid] (2026-01-15 10:54):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，主线还是做半导体吗，还是看卫星ai[s:ac:晕]出去打野亏嘛了还是得回狼窝[/quote]<br/>对  半导体设备<br/>至少上半年是  下半年找材料", "lou": 97, "content_length": 41, "reply_to": 854653118, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768446012}, {"pid": 854654650, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 40, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-15 11:04", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "有些业绩设备压不住了  你们注意不要卖飞了", "lou": 98, "content_length": 38, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768446255}, {"pid": 854656192, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 78, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-15 11:14", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[img]./mon_202601/15/jmQ9951-908nKaT1kSeb-1j.jpg[/img]<br/>个股不能漏给你们  但是ETF应该没问题<br/>我这个是后面170换过来的  因为体量问题。持仓就在10%左右 上去了 减一点 下来了 买一点  每天挂几个量化单子做做差价。你们资金小的 我觉得170更好 爆发力度大很多。", "lou": 99, "content_length": 217, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202601/15/jmQ9951-908nKaT1kSeb-1j.jpg", "size": 10, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202601/15", "name": "jmQ9951-908nKaT1kSeb-1j.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "56"}], "14": {"13": 1}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768446841}], "__T": {"fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "topic_misc": null, "subject": "自立自强，科学技术打头阵", "locked": 0, "recommend": 0, "quote_to": null, "quote_from": 0, "type": 36, "replies": 155484, "authorid": 150058, "postdate": 1768179906, "lastpost": 1782109184, "jdata": null, "author": "-阿狼-", "lastposter": "zippo578", "digest": 0, "lastmodify": 1782109187, "tpid": 0, "post_misc_var": {"content_length": 412, "fid": 706, "comment_id": ",854270755,860174433", "14": {"17": 1, "14": 4, "13": 4, "12": 1}, "16": "63335896,19412700,26652007,67067074,20672033,66881586,67068843,66199622,60819388,60409766,67057614,60264977,61082281,42701832,66998841,61574956,61272875,67082978,66949654,65530601,60630412,60240136,66038632,63481990,61973100,60192597,66985104,19043499,39108806,41714633,7046671,65647302,40696141,3481707,654677,39235785,66063392,39314790,67071606,66251279,42126891,61602239,4785041,4299561